Servers\Game All DB Lucky\Luckycoin\luckucoin 177\QueryHistory\299<|||>1<|||>2022-03-07 14:20:50|luckycoin_report|0|SELECT a.*, MAX(a.gameupdate) AS lastupdate, (a.gamesend - a.gamerecv) AS cashflow, b.cntwinner AS gamewinner, c.cntloser AS gameloser, d.cntduer AS gameduer, (b.cntwinner*100/a.gameccuid) AS gamewinper, (c.cntloser*100/a.gameccuid) AS gamelosper, (d.cntduer*100/a.gameccuid) AS gamedueper, (IFNULL(zzz.sumevent, 0) + IFNULL(zzzz.sumevent, 0)) AS allevent FROM game_sicbo_daily a LEFT JOIN ( SELECT gamedate, COUNT(gameidx) AS cntwinner FROM game_sicbo_user WHERE (gamebetdiv > 0) AND (gameexclude = 0) AND (gameidx <> 0) GROUP BY gamedate ) b ON (a.gamedate = b.gamedate) LEFT JOIN ( SELECT gamedate, COUNT(gameidx) AS cntloser FROM game_sicbo_user WHERE (gamebetdiv < 0) AND (gameexclude = 0) AND (gameidx <> 0) GROUP BY gamedate ) c ON (a.gamedate = c.gamedate) LEFT JOIN ( SELECT gamedate, COUNT(gameidx) AS cntduer FROM game_sicbo_user WHERE (gamebetdiv = 0) AND (gameexclude = 0) AND (gameidx <> 0) AND (gamecnt <> 0) GROUP BY gamedate ) d ON (a.gamedate = d.gamedate) LEFT JOIN ( SELECT rank_conclude AS gamedate, SUM(value_pay_coupon) AS sumevent FROM tb_rank_summary_luckygames WHERE (rank_conclude <> '0000-00-00') AND (rank_game = 'Sicbo') AND (YEAR(rank_conclude) = 2022) AND (MONTH(rank_conclude) = 03) GROUP BY rank_conclude ) zzz ON a.gamedate = zzz.gamedate LEFT JOIN ( SELECT rank_conclude AS gamedate, SUM(value_pay_coupon) AS sumevent FROM tb_rank_summary_luckygames_new WHERE (rank_conclude <> '0000-00-00') AND (rank_game = 'Sicbo') AND (YEAR(rank_conclude) = 2022) AND (MONTH(rank_conclude) = 03) GROUP BY rank_conclude ) zzzz ON a.gamedate = zzzz.gamedate WHERE (YEAR(a.gamedate) = 2022) AND (MONTH(a.gamedate) = 03) GROUP BY a.gamedate ORDER BY gamedate;
